Steps to Create Jenkins as Container inside Docker and run it(Docker present in my windows laptop)::-
================================================================================================
Step 1: Remove existing Jenkins container
docker stop karapada-school-jenkins
docker rm karapada-school-jenkins
C:\Users\niran>docker stop karapada-school-jenkins
karapada-school-jenkins

C:\Users\niran>docker rm karapada-school-jenkins
karapada-school-jenkins

Step 2: Run Jenkins WITH Docker CLI installation
Run exactly this:
docker run -d ^
  -p 8080:8080 ^
  -p 50000:50000 ^
  -v jenkins_home:/var/jenkins_home ^
  -v //var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock ^
  -u root ^
  --name karapada-school-jenkins ^
  jenkins/jenkins:lts-jdk17

C:\Users\niran>docker run -d ^
