=>Once jenkins ready , execute below command::- NEXT STEPS (DO THESE IN ORDER)
STEP 1: Open Jenkins & Initial Setup
Open browser:http://localhost:8080
If it asks for password: docker exec karapada-school-jenkins \ cat /var/jenkins_home/secrets/initialAdminPassword

root@74dae4734b78:/# docker exec karapada-school-jenkins \
cat /var/jenkins_home/secrets/initialAdminPassword
f06f7d1172be4ad6955712db81feb2ff
root@74dae4734b78:/#
=>paste this password in default and create new user for jenkins , once done start jenkins...
=>Install Required Jenkins Plugins
Go to: Manage Jenkins â†’ Plugins â†’ Available->Install:âœ… Docker Pipeline
=>Then click build now in jenkins..

Restart/Start/Stop jenkins::-
----------------------------
docker restart karapada-school-jenkins (cmd) or http://localhost:8080/restart
docker stop karapada-school-jenkins
docker start karapada-school-jenkins















